  <article class="terminal" aria-label="About me in terminal style">
    <div class="terminal-bar">
      <span class="terminal-dot"></span>
      <span class="terminal-dot"></span>
      <span class="terminal-dot"></span>
      <span class="terminal-title">yannik@omarchy ~ zsh</span>
    </div>

    <p><span class="t-prompt">yannik@omarchy</span> <span class="t-prompt">~</span> <span class="t-cmd">cat about.md</span></p>
    <br />
    <p class="t-green">## Software Architect</p>
    <br />
    <p class="t-out">I focus on transforming complex monolithic web systems into</p>
    <p class="t-out">dynamic, interconnected micro-frontend architectures.</p>
    <br />
    <p class="t-out"><span class="t-blue">Expertise:</span> Module Federation · Rspack ecosystem · Distributed systems</p>
    <p class="t-out"><span class="t-blue">OS:</span> Arch Linux (btw)</p>
    <p class="t-out"><span class="t-blue">Editor:</span> Neovim</p>
    <p class="t-out"><span class="t-blue">Hobbies:</span> Trail running · Reading · Cooking for humans</p>
    <br />
